restaurants_1:
A researcher developed an algorithm to predict the outcome of health inspections in different restaurants using the text of the restaurant’s online reviews. They collaborate with the city government to use the algorithm to make decisions on which restaurants to inspect, and also post the results of health inspections on the review website. The prediction algorithm was published online, and the review platform publicly posts some subsets of their internal data (including reviews) for research.
